{"id": "1428843294036721754", "channel_id": "1428843294036721754", "type": 0, "author_id": "104682949340848128", "author_name": "aleksanteri", "author_bot": false, "content": "So I've played through the first chapter over the last couple days and I think I'm sticking with the game for a while, it's pretty solid and quite fun. Though I've heard it gets pretty hard later on.\nAlready managed to pull the following units, decided to focus on Caro and Aequor realms. Should I keep pulling on the standard Aqueor banner to get more copies/more Aqueor characters, or should I switch to pulling for more Caro.\nWhat teams can I build with the characters from the standard 2 banners (or even just from what I have atm).\nAlso how worth is it to pull on the novice 5 guaranteed SSR banner? I don't really know how good the characters in any of those banners are so, Is it better to just buy a sub and wait for a while to get limiteds instead?", "timestamp": "2025-10-17T20:33:07.923000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1428843294468604075", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 891052, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1428843294036721754/1428843294468604075/image.png?ex=69ccd844&is=69cb86c4&hm=9b80b615c0e94168b15551b2c22d50b9e1877c134d28a7e6895bd385b2f356cc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1428843294036721754", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Pull Direction/Account Building advice.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
